categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars: Empire at War

nodes.text: The Twi'lek Dancer was an Interceptor IV-class Frigate in the service of Tyber Zann and the Zann Consortium. Unlike most ships in its class, the Twi'lek Dancer made use of a cloaking device to give it an added level of defense against detection.
The Twi'lek Dancer was cut from the game Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption.
